WEBVTT

00:01.935 --> 00:03.670
<i>PREVIOUSLY ON "THE HAVES</i>
<i>AND THE HAVE NOTS"...</i>

00:03.670 --> 00:05.839
MONEY WILL GET YOU THIS.

00:05.839 --> 00:07.541
EVERYBODY,
THIS IS A GOOD FRIEND OF MINE.

00:07.541 --> 00:08.575
THIS IS CANDACE.
HI.

00:08.575 --> 00:09.710
NICE TO MEET YOU ALL.

00:09.710 --> 00:11.177
SO, DOES THAT MEAN
I'M HIRED?

00:11.177 --> 00:13.413
