YOU HAVEN'T MET MY FAMILY.

00:13.413 --> 00:15.315
AMANDA, SHE'S OUR DAUGHTER.
SHE CUTS HERSELF.

00:15.315 --> 00:17.083
WYATT, HE'S OUR SON.
HE'S IN REHAB.

00:17.083 --> 00:19.185
WHAT KIND OF CON OR GAME
ARE YOU RUNNING NOW?

00:19.185 --> 00:21.154
YOU LOVE ME
AS MUCH AS I LOVE YOU.

00:21.154 --> 00:22.656
YOU GOT IT.
MY FIRST TOW TRUCK.

00:22.656 --> 00:24.390
SOON I'M GONNA HAVE
A FLEET OF THEM.

00:24.390 --> 00:26.860
SHE FINDS OUT I MORTGAGED
THIS HOUSE FOR YOU, SHE'S
GONNA BE DEVASTATED.

00:26.860 --> 00:28.829
YOU WILL HAVE SEVEN DAYS
TO VACATE THE PREMISES.

00:28.829 --> 00:30.330
I WANT $100,000.

00:30.330 --> 00:32.065
YOU ARE RUNNING
FOR GOVERNOR!

00:32.065 --> 00:34.901
Veronica: NOW, JIM WAS HAVING
AN AFFAIR WITH CANDACE YOUNG.

00:34.901 --> 00:37.403
SHE WAS BLACKMAILING HIM
FOR $100,000 AND A CAR.

00:37.403 --> 00:41.341
YOU DELIVERED THAT CAR
WITH TWO KILOS OF COCAINE IN IT.

00:41.341 --> 00:43.343
APPARENTLY ALL THE EVIDENCE
WENT MISSING.

00:43.343 --> 00:45.178
WHAT DO YOU THINK
ABOUT JEFFREY?

00:45.178 --> 00:46.412
THAT MAN IS GAY.

00:46.412 --> 00:48.915
WHY DO YOU ALWAYS HAVE
TO TOUCH ME WHEN YOU TALK TO ME?

00:48.915 --> 00:51.284
I AM CLEAN.
WELL, THEN STAY CLEAN!

00:51.284 --> 00:53.086
I'M SCHEDULED FOR SURGERY
IN THE MORNING.

00:53.086 --> 00:54.621
THEY'RE GOING TO REMOVE
MY BREAST.

00:54.621 --> 00:56.523
Candace: SO, YOU'RE GONNA GO
TO THE PROFESSOR

00:56.523 --> 00:59.259
AND CONVINCE HIM
TO GIVE YOU A MAKE‐UP TEST.

00:59.259 --> 01:00.861
OH, MAN.
AMANDA.

01:00.861 --> 01:03.136
YOUR HUSBAND AND I HAVE BEEN
HAVING AN AFFAIR.

01:03.136 --> 01:05.371
YOUR NAME IS NINE.

01:05.371 --> 01:08.208
WELL, I SAW THE PREGNANCY TEST
IN THE BATHROOM.

01:08.208 --> 01:10.076
I JUST WANT YOU TO TAKE CARE
OF THIS BABY.

01:10.076 --> 01:11.645
HOW MUCH DO YOU WANT?

01:11.645 --> 01:14.080
I'M HIS FATHER.
MR. WATSON'S MY DADDY?

01:14.080 --> 01:16.482
WY, TELL ME THAT YOU LOVE ME.
I'M NOT GAY!

01:16.482 --> 01:17.450
WYATT, NO!

01:17.450 --> 01:19.052
Wyatt:
SO, I TOOK MY CAR...

01:21.121 --> 01:22.723
I KILLED HIM. HE WAS
BENDING DOWN, CHANGING
A TIRE. I DIDN'T ‐‐

01:22.723 --> 01:24.558
HANNA, GET OUT OF HERE.
YOU DIDN'T HEAR A THING.

01:24.558 --> 01:26.226
I'M GAY.
I WILL NEVER...

01:26.226 --> 01:28.461
BE OKAY WITH THAT.

01:28.461 --> 01:31.064
YOUR GRANDFATHER'S WILL.
$12 MILLION.

01:31.064 --> 01:32.566
WE HAVE TO SUE
YOUR PARENTS.

01:32.566 --> 01:33.934
SHE IS NOT YOUR FRIEND.

01:33.934 --> 01:36.570
YOU ARE A PAWN,
AND YOU DON'T EVEN KNOW IT.

01:56.757 --> 01:59.025
COME ON.

01:59.025 --> 02:00.667
OKAY.

02:00.667 --> 02:03.403
WHAT IS IT?

02:03.403 --> 02:05.739
ARE YOU SURE THIS IS
THE RIGHT THING TO DO?

02:05.739 --> 02:06.973
AMANDA.

02:06.973 --> 02:09.442
I'M SORRY, CANDACE.
I'M JUST NOT SURE.

02:09.442 --> 02:12.513
WE TALKED ABOUT THIS
ALL THE WAY OVER HERE.

02:12.513 --> 02:16.016
I KNOW, BUT SUING MY PARENTS
FOR MY INHERITANCE, IT'S ‐‐

02:16.016 --> 02:18.317
IF I KNOW YOUR PARENTS
LIKE I KNOW MOST PEOPLE,

02:18.317 --> 02:20.020
THEY WON'T WANT YOU
TO SUE THEM.

02:20.020 --> 02:22.022
THEY WILL FIND A WAY
TO FIGURE THIS OUT.

02:22.022 --> 02:23.890
YOU DON'T KNOW MY MOM.

02:23.890 --> 02:26.026
UH, YES.
I DO.

02:26.026 --> 02:27.628
[ CHUCKLES ]

02:27.628 --> 02:30.496
WYATT HAS ALWAYS BEEN
THE TROUBLE CHILD, NOT ME.

02:30.496 --> 02:33.399
AND NOW IT'S YOUR TURN TO CAUSE
SOME TROUBLE.

02:33.399 --> 02:34.535
IT'S YOUR MONEY.

02:34.535 --> 02:36.803
I KNOW.

02:36.803 --> 02:38.572
BUT I DON'T KNOW
HOW TO HANDLE MONEY.

02:38.572 --> 02:41.241
IT'S ‐‐ IT'S EASY.
I'LL SHOW YOU.

02:41.241 --> 02:43.510
OKAY, I GET IT.

02:43.510 --> 02:45.345
YOU DON'T TRUST ME.

02:45.345 --> 02:47.180
NO, THAT'S NOT IT.

02:47.180 --> 02:49.182
THEN PLEASE TELL ME
WHAT IT IS.

02:49.182 --> 02:51.652
THIS IS $12 MILLION.

02:51.652 --> 02:55.021
MAYBE IT'S BEST IF THEY KEEP IT
AND I JUST LET THEM INVEST IT

02:55.021 --> 02:57.924
AND MAKE SURE IT'S THERE
WHEN I ACTUALLY NEED IT.

02:57.924 --> 02:59.560
BUT YOU NEED IT NOW.

02:59.560 --> 03:01.835
I DON'T NEED IT NOW.

03:01.835 --> 03:03.670
OKAY.

03:03.670 --> 03:06.372
YOUR MOTHER TOLD YOU
THAT SHE WAS CUTTING YOU OFF

03:06.372 --> 03:08.208
BECAUSE YOU'RE LIVING
WITH ME.

03:08.208 --> 03:11.011
ARE YOU READY TO MOVE BACK
IN THERE

03:11.011 --> 03:13.279
