TO GO THROUGH LAW SCHOOL?

03:13.279 --> 03:16.216
I COULD GET A JOB AT THE LIBRARY
ON CAMPUS.

03:16.216 --> 03:18.018
I SAW AN AD.

03:18.018 --> 03:20.420
THAT'S $8 AN HOUR.

03:20.420 --> 03:22.756
I CAN INTERN
AT A LAW FIRM.

03:22.756 --> 03:25.125
AMANDA.
[ CLEARS THROAT ]

03:25.125 --> 03:27.260
