IF YOU DON'T WANT TO DO THIS.

03:34.400 --> 03:37.003
BUT IT'S YOUR MONEY.

03:37.003 --> 03:40.173
YOUR GRANDFATHER LEFT IT
TO YOU.

03:40.173 --> 03:43.877
YOU CAN OPEN ANOTHER TRUST,
ONE THAT YOU CONTROL,

03:43.877 --> 03:46.079
