AMANDA.

04:01.868 --> 04:04.004
YOU WILL BE THE ONE
IN CONTROL.

04:04.004 --> 04:06.439
JUST YOU.

04:06.439 --> 04:07.941
REALLY?

04:07.941 --> 04:08.942
YES.

04:08.942 --> 04:11.812
NOW, DON'T WORRY, OKAY?

04:11.812 --> 04:14.915
