YOU KNOW?

04:18.919 --> 04:20.687
NO, I‐I WANT TO.

04:20.687 --> 04:22.122
LET'S DO IT.

04:22.122 --> 04:24.190
ARE YOU SURE?

04:24.190 --> 04:25.792
YES.

04:25.792 --> 04:27.761
OKAY.

04:27.761 --> 04:30.430
I NEED YOU TO FIND
ALL THE STRENGTH

04:30.430 --> 04:33.733
RIGHT NOW
IN YOUR BODY.

04:33.733 --> 04:35.201
OKAY.

04:35.201 --> 04:37.336
BECAUSE THIS IS ABOUT
YOUR INDEPENDENCE.

04:37.336 --> 04:38.638
OKAY.

04:38.638 --> 04:40.306
OKAY.

04:40.306 --> 04:43.143
YEAH, LET'S GO IN.

04:43.143 --> 04:44.645
DAMN IT, JIM!
ENOUGH OF THIS!

04:44.645 --> 04:46.312
WHY ARE YOU SO PROTECTIVE
OF HIM?

04:46.312 --> 04:47.814
WELL, IF I HAD BEEN
MORE PROTECTIVE OF HIM,

04:47.814 --> 04:49.516
NONE OF THIS WOULD BE HAPPENING,
NOW WOULD IT?

04:49.516 --> 04:51.151
SO, NOW IT'S MY FAULT?
YES, IT'S YOUR FAULT.

04:51.151 --> 04:53.219
YOU WERE SUPPOSED TO BE AT
CAMP WITH HIM THAT SUMMER, JIM.

04:53.219 --> 04:55.556
OH, GIVE IT A REST, KATHERYN.
YOU LEFT HIM THERE.

04:55.556 --> 04:57.490
YOU WERE WITH FOUR!
WHERE THE HELL WERE YOU?

04:57.490 --> 04:59.025
WHERE WAS MOMMY
WHEN HE NEEDED HER THE MOST?

04:59.025 --> 05:00.527
DON'T YOU EVER PUT YOUR HANDS
ON HIM AGAIN.

05:00.527 --> 05:01.702
HE'S MY SON, TOO.

05:01.702 --> 05:03.303
I CAN DO WHATEVER
THE HELL I WANT TO HIM.

05:03.303 --> 05:05.071
OH, DON'T REMIND ME.

05:05.071 --> 05:07.841
ARE YOU FORGETTING THAT HE
ALSO HAS YOUR MISERABLE LINEAGE,

05:07.841 --> 05:09.976
YOUR BLOOD RUNNING THROUGH
HIS VEINS?

05:09.976 --> 05:11.211
ARE YOU FORGETTING THAT?

05:11.211 --> 05:12.713
THE APPLE DOESN'T FALL
VERY FAR FROM THE TREE,

05:12.713 --> 05:13.714
DOES IT, KATHERYN?

05:13.714 --> 05:15.481
ARE YOU REFERRING TO MY FATHER?
YES.

05:15.481 --> 05:17.150
YOUR FATHER WAS
A RAGING ALCOHOLIC.

05:17.150 --> 05:18.585
HE WAS A DRUNK.
