05:18.585 --> 05:20.186
NO, NO, NO.
YOU DON'T REFER TO HIM.

05:20.186 --> 05:21.387
YOU REFER TO YOURSELF, JIM.

05:21.387 --> 05:23.389
BECAUSE THE APPLE DOESN'T FALL
FAR FROM THE TREE

05:23.389 --> 05:25.325
BECAUSE YOUR TREE IS ON THE SIDE
OF A HILL.

05:25.325 --> 05:27.093
SO HE IS AS FAR AWAY FROM
ANYTHING THAT I HAVE EVER KNOWN.

05:27.093 --> 05:29.195
OUR SON WAS DRIVING
UNDER THE INFLUENCE OF
WHO THE HELL KNOWS WHAT!

05:29.195 --> 05:30.831
I KNOW THAT! YOU DON'T HAVE TO
KEEP SAYING IT!

05:30.831 --> 05:31.932
JUST LIKE YOUR FATHER

05:31.932 --> 05:34.067
AND MISERABLE, MISERABLE DAD
THAT YOU HAD.

05:34.067 --> 05:36.069
NOW WE HAVE TO LIVE
WITH THIS BECAUSE ‐‐

05:36.069 --> 05:37.938
