THIS IS FINE.

06:38.004 --> 06:40.907
BUT PLEASE JUST...GO.

06:40.907 --> 06:42.442
I WILL.

06:42.442 --> 06:44.645
SOON ENOUGH.

06:49.415 --> 06:51.785
THIS LITTLE BITCH
IS INSANE.

06:51.785 --> 06:52.853
MOM!

06:52.853 --> 06:54.788
SHUT UP, AMANDA.

06:54.788 --> 06:58.525
YOU HAVE NO IDEA
WHAT YOU'RE STANDING NEXT TO.

06:58.525 --> 07:00.460
[ SIGHS ]

07:00.460 --> 07:02.135
GET OUT OF MY HOUSE.

07:02.135 --> 07:05.371
NO.
SHE'S NOT GOING ANYWHERE.

07:05.371 --> 07:07.273
MOM, I'VE NEVER HEARD
YOU BE THIS RUDE TO ANYONE.

07:07.273 --> 07:08.975
