YOU'VE NEVER HEARD ME TALK

07:08.975 --> 07:10.511
TO ONE OF YOUR FATHER'S ‐‐
KATHERYN.

07:10.511 --> 07:12.613
WHAT?
SHUT UP.

07:14.648 --> 07:17.217
GET HER THE HELL OUT
OF MY HOUSE.

07:17.217 --> 07:19.553
[ SIGHS ]

07:19.553 --> 07:21.487
CANDACE, MY WIFE AND I

07:21.487 --> 07:22.989
ARE HAVING A DISCUSSION
OF A FAMILY NATURE.

07:22.989 --> 07:24.691
IT'S REALLY NONE
OF YOUR CONCERN.

07:24.691 --> 07:26.292
IS IT WYATT?

07:27.894 --> 07:29.963
[ SIGHS ]
IT'S ALWAYS WYATT.

07:29.963 --> 07:31.565
YES, IT'S WYATT.

07:31.565 --> 07:34.801
