FOR ANYTHING.

07:43.009 --> 07:45.512
WHAT DO YOU NEED, SWEETHEART?
WHAT IS IT?

07:45.512 --> 07:46.713
IT DOES NOT MATTER.

07:46.713 --> 07:49.315
WHAT IS SHE DOING HERE?

07:49.315 --> 07:51.518
