AREN'T YOU?

08:00.701 --> 08:03.003
THIS IS YOU.

08:03.003 --> 08:05.238
YOU.

08:05.238 --> 08:06.673
ALL OVER HER.

08:06.673 --> 08:09.075
ME?
OH, YES.

08:09.075 --> 08:12.445
SHE'S SO SMUG AND DISRESPECTFUL
TO ME NOW THAT SHE'S ‐‐

08:12.445 --> 08:14.715
BECOMING A WOMAN.

08:14.715 --> 08:17.383
NOT YOUR LITTLE GIRL.

08:17.383 --> 08:19.620
SPEAKING HER MIND,

08:19.620 --> 08:23.423
TELLING YOU SHE HAS HOPES
AND DREAMS AND THOUGHTS.

08:23.423 --> 08:25.091
WOW.

08:25.091 --> 08:26.527
WHAT A NOVEL IDEA.

08:26.527 --> 08:27.928
INDEPENDENCE.

08:27.928 --> 08:30.931
AND I SUPPOSE
YOU'RE A WOMAN.

08:30.931 --> 08:33.700
