WHO WILL ATTEST TO THAT.

08:35.468 --> 08:36.937
ARE YOU REFERRING TO JIM?

08:36.937 --> 08:39.305
KATHERYN, STOP IT.

08:39.305 --> 08:42.509
I BELIEVE
SHE DECIDED TO MAKE

08:42.509 --> 08:45.445
