IN MY LIVING ROOM, JIM.

08:45.445 --> 08:50.150
AND I WILL SHOW HER HOW TO PLAY
THE GAME.

08:50.150 --> 08:52.085
SHALL WE?

08:52.085 --> 08:56.322
MAKE YOUR MOVE.

08:56.322 --> 08:58.124
WHAT'S GOING ON?

08:58.124 --> 09:00.060
YOU SHOULD ASK
YOUR FATHER.

09:00.060 --> 09:02.536
KATHERYN,
YOU SHUT YOUR MOUTH RIGHT NOW

09:02.536 --> 09:06.106
OR I WILL SHUT IT FOR YOU,
SO HELP ME.

09:06.106 --> 09:08.408
AMANDA, YOUR MOTHER AND I

09:08.408 --> 09:10.043
ARE HAVING
A LITTLE FAMILY DISCUSSION.

09:10.043 --> 09:12.278
AS SOON AS IT'S OVER,
I PROMISE I WILL CALL YOU

09:12.278 --> 09:16.382
