ANYTHING YOU WANT.

09:16.382 --> 09:18.552
FINE.

09:18.552 --> 09:20.521
FINE.
NO.

09:20.521 --> 09:22.355
NO?

09:22.355 --> 09:24.490
YOU HEARD ME.

09:24.490 --> 09:25.659
IT'S FINE, CANDACE.

09:25.659 --> 09:27.861
YES, CANDACE,
IT'S FINE.

09:27.861 --> 09:31.031
