09:31.031 --> 09:33.433
YOU ALWAYS DO THIS.

09:33.433 --> 09:37.237
YOU ALWAYS WALK AWAY
OR GIVE IN.

09:37.237 --> 09:40.641
AND THEN I HAVE TO LISTEN TO
HOW UNHAPPY YOU ARE ALL NIGHT.

09:40.641 --> 09:43.143
NOT TONIGHT.

09:43.143 --> 09:45.211
THE ANSWER IS NOW.

09:45.211 --> 09:46.813
JIM.

09:46.813 --> 09:49.215
THEY DON'T CARE.
MAKE THEM.

09:49.215 --> 09:52.686
GET...OUT...OF...HERE.

09:55.188 --> 09:57.423
STAND UP STRAIGHT,
AMANDA.

09:57.423 --> 09:59.192
