10:01.267 --> 10:04.938
NOW TELL THEM NO.

10:11.845 --> 10:14.347
NO.

10:14.347 --> 10:17.551
WOW.

10:17.551 --> 10:19.753
JIM.

10:21.722 --> 10:24.558
OUR LITTLE AMANDA HAS
REALLY COME INTO HER OWN

10:24.558 --> 10:26.527
SINCE SHE'S BEEN
WITH THE CHRONOLOGICAL.

10:26.527 --> 10:28.128
