REAL GOOD.

11:48.181 --> 11:50.283
GLADLY. HERE.

11:50.283 --> 11:53.019
WHAT'S THIS?

11:53.019 --> 11:55.321
YOU'RE A JUDGE.

11:55.321 --> 11:57.591
