WHEN YOU'VE BEEN SERVED.

11:59.926 --> 12:01.702
HAVE A GREAT DAY.

12:01.702 --> 12:04.037
HMM.

12:11.912 --> 12:13.914
WHAT IS IT?

12:13.914 --> 12:18.619
IT SEEMS OUR SWEET
LITTLE...INDEPENDENT AMANDA

12:18.619 --> 12:20.587
